  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      for some patients with Crohn's diseases，whether prophylactic abdominal drainage is necessary
      need further exploration. the present study is focusing on the necessity of prophylactic
      abdominal drainage in CD patients after surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
